features: LARGE KITCHEN UTENSILS WITH STAINLESS HANDLE If you've grown tired of small kitchenware that resembles children's toys, this large kitchen tools set is perfect for you. The silicone head combined with the high-quality stainless steel handle ensures lightweight and durable for everyday use. The container is big enough to fit everything back in easily. Stainless steel handles are not only corrosive-proof but also do not need to worry about fading or wear

NO GAPS & DISHWASHER SAFE Strong seamless welding design which is a major plus as there aren't any cracks or ridges to catch food or harbor anything that makes it super easy to clean. The sturdy silicone surface eliminates the worry about damage caused by machine washing to the product, Just put it in the dishwasher after use, and you will get a new set. This cookware utensils set has everything you need, It’s an ideal gift for Mother’s Day, Christmas, as a housewarming present, and more.

FOOD GRADE SILICONE & NO PLASTIC: There is no trace of plastic in the entire construction. Each cooking utensil is made entirely of food-grade silicone, BPA-free, and odorless, We know that this is a health issue that concerns you and your family, So We strictly control the production and quality of these cooking utensils. NOTE: It must be soaked for half an hour when it is used for the first time, and then exposed to the air for about 3 hours, the original smell of silica gel will disappear

NEVER WARP HIGHLY HEAT RESISTANT One of the best things about Umite Chef silicone spatula kitchen utensils is their ability to withstand heat safely, Each utensil is heat-resistant up to whopping 446°F and won’t melt (even leave it in the pot for a while) and our spatula head won't even become knicked or warped even at those extreme temperatures. This silicone cooking utensil does not react with food or beverages and will not retain odors or colors when you use it for stirring-based food product

26 PCS COOKING UTENSILS WITH HOLDER - The Utensil Set includes everything you need to cook that perfect dish, you don't need to spend a fortune to buy each one individually. Includes Slotted Spatula, Slotted Spoon, Flexible Spatula, Slotted Turner, Solid Turner, Pasta Server, Solid Spoon, Kitchen Tongs, Draining Spoon, Whisk, Egg Separator, Deep Soup Ladle, large Spatula, Brush, measuring cups and spoons set, Spreader Spatula, Large Holder
